											<li class="list-group-item">■	The clinical instructor</li>
											<li class="list-group-item">■	The clinical site</li>
											<li class="list-group-item">■	The academic program</li>
											<li class="list-group-item">■	The patient</li>
										</ul>
  									</div>
								
								
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Analyze how a clinical education program can benefit your staff and site</li>
							</ul>
  						</div>
  					</li>
