  						<div class="panel-body">
							<ul class="list-group">
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Describe best practices and guidelines for clinical education sites</li>
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Outline the legal document requirements to become a clinical site</li>
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Plan the steps necessary to prepare for a student’s arrival at your facility</li>
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Develop a clinical curriculum to guide your students’ experiences at your facility</li>
							</ul>
  						</div>
  					</li>
  					<li class="list-group-item">●	Teaching and Learning Principles
  						<div class="panel-body">
							<ul class="list-group">
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Understand current teaching and learning theories as they apply to best practice in the clinical setting.</li>
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Describe characteristics of the adult learner.</li>
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Differentiate between domains of learning.</li>
							</ul>
  						</div>
  					</li>
  					<li class="list-group-item">●	Behavior Objectives and Time Saving Ideas
  						<div class="panel-body">
							<ul class="list-group">
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Apply the understanding of behavioral objectives to their clinical setting</li>
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Implement active learning strategies</li>
							</ul>
  						</div>
  					</li>
  					<li class="list-group-item">●	Assessing Clinical Readiness and Enhancing Clinical Learning
  						<div class="panel-body">
							<ul class="list-group">
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Determine the most appropriate way to assess clinical readiness and enhance clinical learning.</li>
							</ul>
  						</div>
  					</li>
  					<li class="list-group-item">●	Clinical Reasoning
  						<div class="panel-body">
							<ul class="list-group">
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Apply concepts of teaching clinical reasoning to the novice to expert learner. </li>
							</ul>
  						</div>
  					</li>
  					<li class="list-group-item">●	Feedback
  						<div class="panel-body">
							<ul class="list-group">
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Understand delivery methods of formative and summative feedback.</li>
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Demonstrate reflective practice strategies.</li>
							</ul>
  						</div>
  					</li>
  					<li class="list-group-item">●	Reflection
  						<div class="panel-body">
							<ul class="list-group">
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Understand the why reflection is important and how it is used in the clinical environment.</li>
								<li class="list-group-item">○	Demonstrate reflective practice strategies and guide students in the process.</li>
							</ul>
  						</div>
  					</li>
				</ul>
  			</div>
